ICOMOON ICONS
-------------

In the new widget we dont use a sprtiesheet or images at all, we use a font file for all of our icons.
We use a service called icomoon in order to create icon files from SVG files.

These are the source files to use when using icomoon to generate icons.

Wiki page:
https://sites.google.com/a/yotpo.com/yotpo-internal-wiki/cms/icon-fonts?pli=1

When updating the fonts file, you must update the selection.json file.
